we cannot apply jee security mechanism for securing the soap services, for enforcing security for soap services we have ws-security specification, which is part of ws-* specification initiate

ws-security works in conjuction with ws-securitypolicy specification.
	
ws-security specification has defined security markup	that should be used for exchaning the authentication data between consumer and provider
ws-securitypolicy = is a language through which the provider express the policies/ security constriants being imposed in accessing the provider

